    specialAbilities: "Tentacles: Twi'leks can use their head tails to communicate in secret with each other, even in a room full of individuals. The complex movement of the tentacles is a 'secret' language that all Twi'leks are fluent in.",
    forcePoints: 0,
    characterPoints: 8,
    move: 10,
    equipment: "Datapad, hold-out blaster (3D+1)",
    capsule: "Toln ne Yerres is 45 standard years old with a bit more paunch on his frame than the average Twi'lek. He started his career as one of Jabba the Hutt's many ryll-running slaves. He proved himself capable, became his supervisor's right-hand man, then framed the Human for embezzlement when his freedom was withheld — watching as Jabba's enforcers dragged him screaming from his office. Toln then expanded his contacts, moved up through Jabba's organization, and took over as Jabba's financial manager on Tatooine — an intensely coveted position. Recognizing the risk of Jabba's capricious anger, Toln eventually convinced Jabba to send him to Cloud City to manage the Holiday Towers and ensure it turned a profit. Toln ne Yerres is implicated in the death of Odea Aurora's mother, whose ship carried stolen goods from Jabba; Toln sent Glongfurrp to deal with the matter.",
    source: "WEG40119 Galaxy Guide 2: Yavin and Bespin p.91"
