    capsule: "Too-Onebee is a highly sophisticated Genetech 2-1B surgical droid — part of an older series remarkable for its intellect and fierce independence. He joined the Alliance after serving on Firro, where he was patching up the populace after Imperial subjugation. He was then seized by Imperial Governor Lord Cuvir as a personal physician. When Rebel agent Tiree killed Cuvir during a covert operation on Wor Tandell, Too-Onebee joined the Alliance. Assigned as chief of surgery at Echo Base, he saved Luke Skywalker's life after Skywalker suffered grievous wampa wounds and exposure in the Hoth wilderness — using a fully prepared bacta tank. He later fitted Skywalker with a cyborg replacement for his severed right hand.",
