    capsule: "Dwin Arnae is a mousy, wiry little man with straight, jet-black hair cut short and beginning to thin. Considered a perfectionist by his crew, his uniform is always spotless, his words carefully chosen, and his crew must be ever attentive. He hopes to set an Imperial record by apprehending the most customs violators, regardless of how minor the infraction. He joined the Imperial Navy early to give the Empire the benefit of his 'extraordinary' abilities but advanced only as far as staff sergeant. When he uncovered a minor infraction by his superiors and reported over their heads, he was removed from the Navy and sent to the Sector Interdiction Office. His crew hates him and will often overlook infractions they discover simply to irritate him — tramp freighters are almost relieved to discover it is Dwin conducting their search.",
