    equipment: "Blaster carbine (4D+2 damage, 3/20/150, hidden behind counter), comlink",
    capsule: "Kai Lup and her husband Tar run Lup's Wares and Supplies (known as 'Lup's General Store'). Despite their fierce, wolf-like appearance, they are both friendly and helpful. The store contains provisions, supplies, and a smattering of machinery, with touch-screen monitors for browsing merchandise catalogs. They charge 90-110% of standard prices, and 120% for medical equipment and weaponry. Readily available goods can be found in stock, most large-city items are available or can be ordered, but specialized or rare products cannot be had here. Illegal transactions are conducted behind a sliding mirror in the bathroom, and private haggling in the rear offices. The Lups have been experiencing trouble with Jabba over protection payments — they would prefer a percentage of weekly gross receipts rather than a flat sum, but Jabba has declined. Congenial lupines, they tend to remember slights and perceived rudeness and do not like anyone poking about in their business.",
