    capsule: "A green-skinned Gamorrean with a pig-like snout, small horns and tusks, and powerful muscles. Gorrt's innate skill as an enforcer was not always recognized out in Jabba's palace beyond the Jundland Wastes. After a brief run-in with an uncooperative store owner, Gorrt's 'finesse' and skill were rewarded with a permanent post in Mos Eisley. He tends to be protective of Akkik, but generally loves to beat on anything smaller than him. The Hutt also owns the rectangular building behind the Townhouse, which serves as barracks for his guards and a garage with room for a small sail barge, an assortment of speeders, and posts to tie up a dozen Dewbacks or Banthas.",
