    characterPoints: 4,
    move: 9,
    equipment: "None listed",
    capsule: "Oxbel is the brother of Labria, a Devaronian who used to work for Slag Flats. Like his brother, Oxbel arrived on Tatooine intending a holiday of gambling and a good time — and like his brother, he has yet to leave. He makes his living keeping his eyes and ears open to news, selling it to whomever would most like to hear it. His favorite spots are outside Docking Bay 94 and the cantina or the Lucky Despot. However, he lacks the talent and ambition of Labria, spending more time downing lum than poking around for information. When he drinks — now a daily habit — he becomes alternately morose and chatty, babbling incoherently about both public and private information. His objective is to keep selling information so he can afford to drink.",
    source: "WEG40069 Galaxy Guide 7: Mos Eisley p.55"
