    capsule: "A tiny, gray-furred Squib biped with tufted ears. Mace has been across the galaxy and is a wealth of useless trivia about species and planets. He agreed to help Aguilae run her droid shop because he owed her money. He is loving every minute of it and is considering opening his own shop, but has no idea what to deal in. Mace seems to be an airhead, judging the importance of things according to Squib values — the love of bargaining. His objective is to honor the Squib tradition by achieving the most convoluted bargains possible.",
