    capsule: "Matt Talon wears the uniform of the First Sun Mobile mercenary unit — light scout-style armor with the company's insignia on the right shoulder. Jet black hair pulled into a tail, with a scar from beneath his right eye to the corner of his mouth. An aura of ill-concealed violence surrounds him. He was an impoverished young man from an agricultural planet who joined the First Sun Mobile until a sector Moff had his stormtroopers butcher the company — Talon was one of about a dozen survivors. After wandering as a bounty hunter, he made contact with the Rebel Alliance and was assigned to work with Thila on the Arkanian Dawn. Before meeting Thila he was on a fast track to the Dark Side, but realizing the Empire's evil has given him purpose. Fiercely loyal to Thila — would interpose his body between her and a blaster bolt.",
    source: "WEG40063 Galaxy Guide 9: Fragments from the Rim p.9"
