    equipment: "Forgery kit, selection of fake IDs, 3 Cybot Galactica 3PO protocol droids, 2 Cybot Galactica XC2 administration droids, hold-out blaster (3D damage), 5,000-12,000 credits",
    capsule: "Kina Margath is a high-powered executive, always immaculately dressed with quiet authority — a born leader. She inherited her business empire fourteen years ago and built Margath's on Elshandruu Pica into a galaxy-wide institution: five-star hotel, casino, bars, conference facilities, private gaming rooms, zero-g swimming and gravball, with over 1,500 full-time staff and three times as many part-timers ('Welcome to Margath's. I am the owner, Kina Margath.'). She quietly despises the Empire for its trade restrictions and lets Rebel agents use her establishments as safehouses — she is a Rebel Foster Agent, collecting orphaned agents and returning them to the Alliance. X-wing pilots are given her name so they have a ground contact if they bail out. The 27th Hour Social Club is the crown jewel of Margath's — it literally never closes, partying 27 hours a day on a planet with a 26-hour day. Its challenge: 'If we don't know it, your tab is on the house!' — has built a drink library of over 14 million concoctions. Elshandruu Pica is a sector capital in Quence Sector.",
    source: "WEG40063 Galaxy Guide 9: Fragments from the Rim p.41-42"
