    capsule: "The First Sun Mobile Regiment is a mercenary repulsorlift infantry regiment that frequently contracts to the Imperial Army, specializing in search-and-destroy missions they call SLAMs (Search, Locate, Annihilate Mission). Often undertakes Base Delta Zero-style objectives: eliminating all assets of production including factories, arable land, mines, and sapient witnesses. Gained a reputation for total ruthlessness and heinous atrocities. After an Imperial Moff had his stormtroopers butcher one of the First Sun's companies for 'exceeding their authority,' the regiment no longer trusts Imperial backup and is investigating alternatives to working for the Empire — though joining the Rebel Alliance is not considered viable. Matt Talon (see Shelvay's Operatives) was a former member before his unit was massacred.",
