    capsule: "The Khuiumin Survivors are the remnants of the Eyttyrmin Batiiv pirate gang, reduced from 8,000 to fewer than 275 by the Imperial Victory-class Star Destroyers Bombard and Crusader. The survivors went into hiding, spending virtually every free moment training to exact revenge. Under Jacob Nive's leadership, they now wear uniforms and maintain strict discipline. They have proportionally twice as many pilots as the Void Demons of Isen IV, all highly experienced in combat and high-speed attack runs. Currently only the corvette Backstab and a handful of starfighters remain operational — the mighty pirate armada of 70+ starfighters, 50 yachts, and 28 corvettes is no more.",
