    capsule: "The Bloodsniffers swoop gang has haunted isolated worlds of Quence Sector for nearly a decade. Their origin is unknown — they simply appeared on the border of a farming community on Xiunsrus one morning, demanded 10,000 credits by afternoon, and destroyed the village when refused. Over 100 riders strong with support crew and hangers-on, they travel world to world targeting isolated communities — cutting communications and extracting whatever booty can be had. They carefully investigate each town to ensure insufficient law enforcement and that reinforcements can't arrive in time. Noted for their bright red swoops and jackets.",
    source: "WEG40063 Galaxy Guide 9: Fragments from the Rim p.69"
