    specialAbilities: "Findsman Ceremonies: Zuckuss uses elaborate and arcane rituals to find his prey, drawing omens from them. Whenever he uses a ritual (minimum 3 hours), he gains +2D to track a target.",
    forcePoints: 0,
    characterPoints: 9,
