    capsule: "Bossk is a member of the warlike Trandoshan species, which has a particularly strong hatred of Wookiees. At the suggestion of his Trandoshan liege lord, young Bossk became a bounty hunter and over the years has become a master with a reputation for skill and ruthlessness. The exploits of one Wookiee named Chewbacca have ignited a burning passion — the desire to bring Chewbacca's pelt to his liege lord. The Wookiee has continually evaded his best attempts at capture, remaining a source of constant frustration. Until another opportunity presents itself, Bossk contents himself with other 'fresh meat.' He specializes in tracking escaped Wookiee slaves and has been known to be 'overzealous' in bringing them to justice.",
    source: "WEG40073 Galaxy Guide 10: Bounty Hunters p.66"
