    capsule: "Alic Surn is one half of a famous brother-sister bounty hunter team. An easygoing gambler who tries to enjoy life to the fullest since he believes it will probably end soon. Only the present and his sister's safety matter. He works hard and plays harder, never worrying about tomorrow. A marked contrast to his intense sister Vika — he handles logistics, piloting, and repairs while she handles the kills. They operate through the Neuvalis Syndicate, hunting in the Inner Rim, paying a 5% cut in exchange for their transport ship, the Widow Maker. In killing situations, Alic always defers to his sister.",
