    capsule: "Tesslar drifted into bounty hunting by accident. Born into poverty in the Outer Rim, he dropped out of school and began stealing speeders. He hooked up with spacer Shamel, stealing speeders for a smuggling ring, and learned he had a knack with a blaster. In time he left Shamel and struck out as an independent Imperial hunter. He has reddish hair and a dark complexion, works alone, and answers only to Imperial authorities. He has an open disgust for independent and guild hunters and has been known to interfere with their hunts.",
