    equipment: "Datapad, heavy blaster pistol (5D), droid disabler, retina disguiser, shipjacking kit",
    capsule: "F'quallix is a rarity among jackers in that he typically plans his operations with an eye towards minimizing injury to the ship's crew. Often his reputation alone is enough to facilitate his hijacking efforts. Knowing they won't be harmed if they surrender, many smugglers and ship's officers will prefer to lose their cargoes rather than their lives. F'quallix has fewer scruples over those he deals with in the black market. He is suspected of being responsible for severe injuries inflicted on several known marketeers with whom his business arrangements have soured over the years. TracSheet: Alias — real name unknown. Typically works with a gang including local enforcers and members of spaceport haulers local. Has a reputation for not harming ship's personnel unless they resist. Muscular build with thick dark brown fur, wears eye protectors suggesting light sensitivity.",
