    specialAbilities: "Natural Armor: Herglic skin gives +1D against physical attacks. Distrust: Because of past dealings with the Empire few consider Herglics reliable or trustworthy. All non-Herglics have an additional +1D when making opposing Perception rolls against Herglics. Gambling Frenzy: Herglics are irresistibly drawn to all forms of games of chance. Any Herglic confronted with any form of gambling must make a Moderate willpower check to avoid the compulsion to join in.",
