    capsule: "Leia Organa Solo is one of the New Republic's most celebrated heroes. Born 28 years ago to a mother she barely remembers and a father she never knew, she was adopted by Bail Organa, Viceroy and Senator of Alderaan. Elected to the Imperial Senate as the youngest Senator until her own record was matched, she became a key figure in the Alliance to Restore the Republic. In the five years since Endor, her diplomatic skills have brought many worlds into the New Republic. She has embraced her Skywalker heritage, becoming Luke's student in the ways of the Force. Using tools once belonging to Ben Kenobi, she constructed her own lightsaber in the wilderness over eight days — completing the task far faster than most Jedi, demonstrating extraordinary natural ability. She married Han Solo and recently gave birth to Force-sensitive twins, Jaina and Jacen. As 'Mal'ary'ush' — daughter and heir of Darth Vader — she commands the sworn loyalty of the Noghri species.",
