    capsule: "Diblen Harleys was born on Coruscant as the child of a privileged bureaucrat, well insulated from Imperial atrocities. Around his 15th birthday, his father revealed the reality of the Empire, telling him it was 'better to stay quiet and protect yourself than die as a dissident.' Shocked at having been brainwashed, Harleys joined the Rebel Alliance. He served as both a starfighter pilot and tactician, with his inspired tactics proving useful at the Battle of Endor. While his first love is flying, his responsibilities have kept him out of the cockpit. Relatively young, he is still treated as inexperienced by fellow officers, though he maintains an easy friendship with Admiral Ackbar and Colonel Derlin. Popular with his troops for his outrageous sense of humor and dedication to protecting their lives. He wears glareshades and a blue gemstone earring.",
    source: "WEG40131 The Thrawn Trilogy Sourcebook p.39"
