    capsule: "Wes Janson has faithfully served the Rebel Alliance and the New Republic with honor and distinction. Stationed at the Tierfon fighter base early in his career, he was tail gunner for Wedge Antilles on Hoth and currently flies back seat for a Y-wing group attached to Rogue Squadron. A 'True Gunner' — stationed in the least protected section of a starfighter, fending off attackers with a single weapon — requiring tremendous skill, courage, and probably an unhealthy dose of recklessness. Average in appearance — so average that New Republic Intelligence has unsuccessfully tried to recruit him for field duty. Popular with his squadron-mates for his quirky sense of humor and near legendary status as a True Gunner, as well as his propensity for starting barroom brawls on shore leave.",
    source: "WEG40131 The Thrawn Trilogy Sourcebook p.41"
