    capsule: "Lieutenant Page hails from Corulag, one of the Imperial Core Worlds, where he grew up as the pampered son of a corrupt Senator. He used his father's wealth to train himself in all forms of combat, then was sent to the Academy where he graduated with honors and was assigned to General Veers' command. After hearing Senator Leia Organa speak at the Council of Galactic Rights, he deserted and joined the Alliance. He served at Echo Base under Major Derlin and was part of General Solo's strike team at Endor. When Derlin accepted promotion, the commandos were offered to Page. He accepted but refused higher rank, admiring Solo and Skywalker who had no use for ranks. His unit adopted the katarn — a predator from Kashyyyk — as their mascot after a Wookiee named Frorral compared the commandos to the creature: invisible until they wanted to be seen, silent until they wanted to be heard, and deadly when they had to be. A totally nondescript-looking man who blends invisibly into any surroundings — the perfect commando.",
