    capsule: "Lt. Kylan DuPre is Admiral Drayson's most trusted aide. He originally served as quartermaster aboard the Stormstrike, a Corellian Corvette serving Chandrila. During a surprise TIE ambush, DuPre threw himself between an overloading power conduit explosion and Drayson, saving the admiral's life. Drayson has since pulled DuPre with him, including to Coruscant. A short, stocky near-human who is highly ambitious — some would say power hungry — he craves promotion and sees Drayson as his fast track to the Admiralty. He is courteous and obedient to superiors but officious, arrogant and callous to those beneath him. He is loathed by the lower ranking officers under his command.",
