    move: 10,
    equipment: "Imperial Navy uniform, blaster pistol (4D), comlink, datapad",
    capsule: "Ensign Rejlii Mithel is the son of the infamous 'Mauler' Mithel, one of Vader's wingmen killed at the Battle of Yavin. Serving aboard the Chimaera as a weapons technician specializing in tractor beam systems, he gained Grand Admiral Thrawn's notice during an encounter with a New Republic vessel. When a Ghtroc freighter disintegrated into reflective particles in a covert shroud gambit, freeing a hidden X-wing, Mithel attempted to counter by switching the tractor beam to 'shear-plane mode' and locking onto the cloud of fragments. The control computer froze, unable to handle the myriad changing variables, and the X-wing escaped. Thrawn, recognizing Mithel's innovative thinking, promoted him to lieutenant and ordered him to find a workable solution to the covert shroud gambit. Mithel is young, energetic and dedicated — typical of the courageous, talented breed Thrawn intended to mold into the backbone of a new Empire.",
    source: "WEG40131 The Thrawn Trilogy Sourcebook p.81"
