    capsule: "Brasck is a Brubb from the planet Baros and one of the major smuggling chiefs operating in the Borderland Regions. A former mercenary recruited by Jabba the Hutt, he grabbed whatever followers he could after the crime lord's demise and set up his own operation. Brasck deals in anything, including kidnapping and slaves, with the Empire and crime organizations as his major clients. He travels aboard his command ship Green Palace, preferring deep space and constant motion to a permanent base. He is afraid of the Empire, especially Grand Admiral Thrawn — he remembers stories of the man from when he was a boy on Baros, when Thrawn found his world and taught it to respect and fear the Empire. He has taken on the bounty for Luke Skywalker but has ordered his operatives not to hurt him too much, feeling a certain debt to the Jedi whose actions allowed him to become a smuggler chief.",
