    equipment: "Sporting blaster (3D+2), comlink, datapad",
    capsule: "Bel Iblis was officially invited to participate in the New Republic after the battle for the Katana fleet. His relationship with Mon Mothma has improved considerably — after years of believing she was consolidating power for its own sake, he finally realized she was terrified of trusting lives to anyone else. Mon Mothma requested his help in the Siege of Coruscant, and under his leadership a bad situation was prevented from becoming a complete rout. His troops from Peregrine's Nest remain at his command and have actively fought on behalf of the New Republic. His character points increased from 32 to 38, reflecting his renewed purpose.",
