    equipment: "Heavy blaster pistol (5D), comlink, knife (STR+1D)",
    capsule: "Irenez is Senator Garm Bel Iblis's chief of security — short, slender, with close-cut graying hair and a thin, friendly face. She is in excellent shape, a fully-trained and battle-hardened warrior. Cheerful and full of humor when circumstances allow, but all business when working — and her business is deadly. She received initial training at the Old Republic Military Academy on Corellia but lost her commission as the Empire gained influence. She worked as a mercenary, eventually forming her own platoon for hire. Her association with Bel Iblis goes back to adolescence — he sponsored her Academy admission. She brought her platoon when he called for soldiers and proved her worth, playing pivotal parts in the raids on Tangrene and Gestron. Now that Peregrine's Nest has joined the New Republic, Irenez longs for one last campaign against the Empire.",
    source: "WEG40131 The Thrawn Trilogy Sourcebook p.100"
