    capsule: "Dravis graduated from the Imperial Academy with honors as a starfighter pilot. His father expected him to join the infamous Scimitar Wing assault group, but Dravis had other plans — he stole a Lambda-class shuttle and fled to the Outer Rim. Persistent rumor cites a Corellian female, an irate father, and something called 'DL-44 nuptials' as the cause. He met and was hired by Billey, who recognized his piloting ability. Of medium height with a muscular build and short brown hair, fairly nondescript. Quick with a joke, hot-tempered and energetic, though his energy doesn't quite make up for his lack of experience. TIE piloting specialization at 9D+1.",
