    capsule: "Very little is known about the smuggler Mazzic, and that's how he likes it. Well known for his suspicious nature and distrust of outsiders. After the death of his friend Lishma at the hands of the Empire, Mazzic became determined to make the Empire think twice. He and other smugglers staged an assault on the Bilbringi shipyards, destroying a Star Destroyer under construction. A Corellian who refuses to discuss his departure from his homeworld — at some point the Empire double-crossed him and a 'friend' was murdered, possibly his wife. He is tall and muscular with long black hair, wearing a skintight black flight suit, heavy blaster pistol, and short black cloak. A no-nonsense individual with no tolerance for deception.",
