    specialAbilities: "Spray: ZeHethbra can project a stinging spray that can blind and stun those within a three-meter radius. All characters within range must make a Difficult willpower roll or take 5D stun damage; if the result is wounded or worse, the character is overcome by the spray and collapses to the ground for one minute.",
