    specialAbilities: "Claws: STR+1D. Teeth: STR+2D. Stealth: +2D when using hide or sneak. Enhanced Senses: +2D when using search. Noghri Martial Arts: +2D when used against someone without this specialization, does STR+1D+2 damage.",
